item.title: Working on My Brand
item.description: Working on my Brand It may sound weird, but each and every one of us have a brand, whether you like it or not. Someone’s branding may completely eclipse most of what we do because they have intentionally developed their brand. What Is Your Brand Your brand how you want to be respresented in your technology community. The following are a few things to chew on. If you answer to any of these questions, you, by default have a brand whether you know it or not.

item.title: Enter 2019 With a Bang
item.description: Transitioning from WordPress to Github Welcome to my first attempt at moving away from WordPress and over to github.io. This will be a trial run. Motivation I wanted to increase my blogs post cadence to more than a few posts a year and leverage MarkDown in the process because that’s what the cool kids are doing. I looked at WP and in order to add the MD plugin, you had to be a Business Plan subscriber at a mere cough cough $25/month.
